Assets.Name: Blokto Park v1.2
Assets.Description:
Get your Bloktober on with BloktoPark. Small indoor park.
Now compatible with 0.0.0.5!
OPTIONAL:
Fix for the decals not showing (wax & wheel marks).
Go to your Session\SessionGame\Config\UserEngine.ini file and add the following lines:

[/Script/Engine.RendererSettings]
r.DBuffer = True

I haven't noticed any issues using this so far but if anything goes wrong try changing the True to False (or delete the lines from your UserEngine.ini).
Assets.Author: JammieDodger
